content.div:
Just because Justin Bieber is now an adult, it doesn't mean he's acting like one. According to insiders, Bieber's birthday party dance-off was rigged so that he could win and remain a happy birthday boy.

--

Well, that didn't take long. Oprah has already sat down with Whitney Houston's family, including Bobbi Kristina and Bobby Brown. Watch a preview of the interview here.

--

Ouch! Photographers mistook Debbie Harry for Lindsay Lohan outside the Mercer Hotel in NYC. Harry is 66; Lohan is 25.

--

Snooki has finally confirmed what we've suspected for weeks: she's pregnant.

--

What's Snooki going to name the pickle in her oven? Here are a few of her favourite baby names.

--

Kris Humphries isn't the only one his family playing the fame game. His little sis, Kaela, just signed a deal with modeling agency FORD for their plus size division.

--

Prince Harry is currently touring Jamaica. While no shirtless pics have surfaced yet, feel free to enjoy this one of him working up a sweat.

--

The Bachelor's Women Tell All episode may have aired earlier this week, but it offered no clues on which gal Ben ends up with. However, judging from these new photos, it looks like both Courtney and Lindzi are out of luck!

--

Bros before hoes? Sistas before mistas? Not if you're Jennifer Aniston and Courteney Cox. It looks like the BFFs may be heading towards splitsville, all because of Aniston's man.

--

In a new MTV special, Demi Lovato bravely admitted that she still struggles with bulimia and cutting.

--

Sources say that Ashton Kutcher and his soon-to-be ex-wife, Demi Moore, have reconnected since her stint in rehab. Expect reconciliation rumours to hit any minute now.

--

Miranda Kerr may be one of the most beautiful girls in the world -- but Chanel somehow managed to mess up her perfect mug! WTF?!

--

It's ten years later, but the cast of American Pie has reunited -- and they still look the exact same.

--

Lindsay Lohan isn't the only one in her family making headlines. LiLo's little sister, Ali, is showing off a dramatic new 'do. Unfortunately, nothing will make us forget her sister's bomb-worthy performance on Saturday Night Live.

--

Jessica Simpson is pulling a Demi Moore and posing nude on a magazine cover.

--

Are you a Marvel comics fan? Well, now you, too, can own your very own Avengers props!

--

Check back to Dose.ca throughout the day for your entertainment fix.
